name: One Night at Basko's - German Youtuber Custom Night
name_original: One Night at Basko's - German Youtuber Custom Night
description:
This is a fangame for GermansnakeGaming, Corrupted, Sev, CreepySmalltalk, Creepypastapunch, TobiToast and Tjulfar.
It's a survival-horrorgame heavily inspired by Five Nights at Freddy's. 

Have fun and pushing your survival-skills to the limit by customizing the difficulty and achieving new (high)scores! ^^
